# ğŸ² FoodAid â€“ MERN Donation & Impact Tracking Platform

FoodAid is a full-stack MERN (MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js) application designed to manage donations, track impact, and connect volunteers, donors, and administrators in food relief efforts.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

### ğŸ‘¥ User Management
- User registration & authentication (JWT-based)
- Protected routes for logged-in users
- User profile creation and update

### ğŸ’° Donations
- Users can make and view donations
- Admins can view all donations
- Tracks donation title, quantity, location, and time created

### ğŸ’š Impact Tracking
- Record how donations helped beneficiaries
- Aggregate reports on the total number of people reached
- Latest impact stories and stats

### ğŸ“Š Admin Dashboard
- View total users, donations, and impact reports
- View latest donations and recent impacts
- View total beneficiaries helped

### ğŸ–¥ï¸ Frontend (React + Vite)
- Clean, responsive user interface
- Authentication and protected views
- Integration with backend APIs
- Dashboard, Profile, Donations, and Impact pages

